						<summary>

						<p>This seems to register an endowment to Tiruviśalūr-Perumāṉaḍigaḷ, of 160 <hi rend="italic">kuḻi</hi> of land to the south of Pāśi-vāykkāl (channel) and north-west of Avaninārāyaṇachaturvēdimaṅgalam, by one Māḍalaṉ Śēndaṉ a resident of the place.</p>						

						</summary>
